---
---

<section id="about">
  <div class="section-inner about-grid">
    <div class="about-image">
      <div class="about-image-placeholder">
        <span>Your photo here</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="about-text">
      <p class="section-label">Who We Are</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">
        A home away from home — for you and your pets.
      </h2>
      <div class="divider"></div>
      <p>
        We're <strong>Callum & Niamh</strong>, a couple from the UK currently
        travelling and house sitting across Australia. With years of experience
        caring for pets and homes, we treat every sit like it's our own.
      </p>
      <p>
        Whether it's a weekend away or a month-long trip, we move in and keep
        everything running smoothly — daily walks, feeding routines, garden care,
        and plenty of love for your animals.
      </p>
      <p>
        We're verified on <strong>Rover</strong> and
        <strong>TrustedHouseSitters</strong>, with over 40 five-star reviews from
        happy pet owners. Your home and pets are in safe hands.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  section {
    padding: 80px 48px;
    background: var(--warm-white);
  }

  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 60px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .about-image-placeholder {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 4 / 5;
    background: var(--gold-pale);
    border-radius: 12px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: var(--brown-light);
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .about-text p {
    color: var(--text-soft);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .about-text p strong {
    color: var(--brown-dark);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    section {
      padding: 60px 24px;
    }

    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 40px;
    }
  }
</style>
